{"tid":2040840,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葉劉淑儀：即使美國暫停對港貿易特殊待遇　影響亦輕微","createTime":"2020-05-29T00:26:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T02:10:17.000Z","uid":137088,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"cf73de0f8eda628725525c92a6e6ac6116379e29","tid":2040840,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:26:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1528825_1_L_20200528103518.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1528825_1_L_20200528103518.jpg&h=4a15ee97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新民黨議員葉劉淑儀認為，即使美國暫停對本港的貿易特殊待遇，只有輕微影響。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀表示，香港對美國的貿易多屬轉口，如果美國對香港本地生產的出口貨品加關稅，只會有輕微影響，而中國經本港的轉口，本身已受中美貿易戰影響，加上美國對本港有極大貿易順差，單在去年已經超過260億美元。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀又指出，美國因「港區國安法」可能制裁本港的消息，並非突如其來，相信市場早有預期，並消化一部分消息，又指全國人大常委為港版國安法立法，目前本港議員及官員沒有角色，根據美國相關的法例，本港議員及官員不符合制裁門檻，又指即使美國強行要制裁，方式不外乎凍結資產或拒發簽證，認為資產可以變賣，不去美國亦非大損失。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528825-20200528.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528825-20200528.htm&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=c74ac3b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528825-20200528.htm&h=86331383\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528825-20200528.htm</a>"},{"pid":"422e0c5c6f390d1aa1a71c94bc3aebb7d18cb571","tid":2040840,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bddbbe376f88eeb5d16a379f3f7fa57d150bd7c5","tid":2040840,"uid":84128,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:42:20.000Z","msg":"既然無乜影響<br />\n咁點解仲要叫美國維持對港政策？"},{"pid":"a2045ba0f0d4739a133a4afd32f8a06f254e0240","tid":2040840,"uid":197441,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"ci